{
  "stem": "16106.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were deported to Russia in big-- in trains, in sealed trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Ossie was one among them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He-- during the-- during the time of the Soviet Union, we couldn't have our big apartments.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We have to share so-- so and so much square feet was allowed, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they had a very big apartment, the Velkins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they had somebody from the NKVD living there with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they got the info, so what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Besides, I didn't tell you that was a-- the that house, which was called the Blue Wonder, the Blue Miracle-- underneath, in the cellar, they had the NKVD doing evil things to people-- that's Blaue Wunder",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew that, what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That we knew-- in Blaue Wunder-- some wonder, it had three stories.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and that NKVD of man-- in those days, it was called NKVD-- came then the next morning and brought me things Ossie left me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He left me 50 rubles, all his savings, his fountain pen, and a lovely book by-- not [NON-ENGLISH], by-- it's called with illustrations by some Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very-- do you ever seen that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a wonderful-- it's 'wonder' something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyhow-- so-- and that was a goodbye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was so upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cried so hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I took my bike and drove out to the trains, but they were all sealed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And never saw those people for 50 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Two years ago, he came to visit with his wife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He brought me the picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Never heard of them-- they were all in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But then afterwards, they-- his mom died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "His-- but they went to school, and he became an architect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he married an architect.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
